Module Hierarchy

  • nflgame: An API to retrieve and read NFL Game Center JSON data.
    • nflgame.alert: A module that provides convenience functions for sending alerts.
    • nflgame.game
    • nflgame.live: The live module provides a mechanism of periodically checking which games are being actively played.
    • nflgame.player
    • nflgame.schedule
    • nflgame.seq
    • nflgame.statmap: The stats module maps statistical category identifiers from NFL.com's GameCenter JSON feed to a representation of what we believe that statistical category means.
